&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The Head of Pricing &amp;amp; Market Access will lead global and U.S. pricing, reimbursement, access, and value strategies across Kymera&#39;s pipeline and future commercial products. Reporting to the Chief Commercial Officer, this executive will play a critical role in maximizing patient access and commercial value by shaping payer, provider, government, and health-system strategies from late-stage development through launch and lifecycle management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a key member of the Commercial Leadership Team, this leader will partner closely with&amp;nbsp;Marketing,&amp;nbsp;Clinical Development, Medical Affairs, Regulatory, HEOR, Market Research, Finance, Business Development, and Corporate Strategy to ensure access considerations are embedded throughout development and commercialization planning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will bring deep immunology&amp;nbsp;expertise, preferably including atopic dermatitis and asthma, along with a proven&amp;nbsp;track record&amp;nbsp;of market access leadership across U.S. and global markets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
